{"tid":1262074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"律政中心後門現況","createTime":"2019-06-27T13:55:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T15:49:57.000Z","uid":115000,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"4f84e3e74a49e9788056f3ad5c813b1413d82b09","tid":1262074,"uid":115000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T13:55:04.000Z","msg":"img]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/dNAa43o.jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdNAa43o.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPHwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=b573bd99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/dNAa43o.jpg[/img]</a><br />\n<br />\n律政後門 2140<br />\n無記者<br />\n無live<br />\n無急救<br />\n無裝備<br />\neven連cam都無<br />\n現場50個人都無<br />\n有咩事都幾危險<br />\n惡犬沖上嚟發生咩事無人會知<br />\n見成個連登無人知咩事<br />\n真係發生咩事嘅話<br />\n希望會仲有人記得呢班敢留底嘅人<br />\n<br />\n我無能力留低<br />\n唔想叫人唔好去<br />\n亦都唔想出聲叫佢地走<br />\n唔奢求有人支持<br />\n只係希望呢班人平平安安<br />\n<br />\nbtw發夢所見"},{"pid":"9d2bc108185027508046ab62ff71d6086aaab73b","tid":1262074,"uid":116709,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T13:56:26.000Z","msg":"總之人多就一齊行， 人少就一齊閃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4d6104c8a7b50cad5505f59d7393ec5ff45bd71","tid":1262074,"uid":202640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T13:57:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"36665e4600bc4fc8a8906920ea992a1a3342c3b3","tid":1262074,"uid":4783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T13:58:09.000Z","msg":"be water<br />\n唔夠人就閃水先<br />\n唔好同佢硬碰"},{"pid":"743d4174f95d5dc899a7f4fbec7ff7683cc63ff3","tid":1262074,"uid":111269,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T13:58:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b2ac0f263e436f3d1f78ce56fd851675dd87967d","tid":1262074,"uid":115000,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T14:15:56.000Z","msg":"更新下現況<br />\n啱啱發夢見到<br />\n<br />\n前門嘅人開始散緊<br />\n有人唔想浪費在場嘅人數<br />\n所以組織一次小遊行<br />\n